---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Contact | freellm.site"
  description="Get in touch with the freellm.site team — report outdated provider info, suggest new providers, or ask questions."
>
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p class="legal-lead">
      We'd love to hear from you — whether you're reporting outdated provider info, suggesting a new provider, or just saying hello.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-cards">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>GitHub Issues</h2>
        <p>Report outdated data, request new providers, or discuss features:</p>
        <p><a href="https://github.com/khushaljethava/freellm-apis/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">Open an issue on GitHub →</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>Contribute</h2>
        <p>Submit a pull request with updated provider or model data:</p>
        <p><a href="https://github.com/khushaljethava/freellm-apis" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link">freellm-apis repository →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Response time</h2>
    <p>We aim to respond to GitHub issues within a few business days. Provider data corrections are typically reviewed and merged within a week.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
